In [299]:
window = 260
sv = [0] * (df_returns.shape[0]-window-1)
count=0

for t in range(261, df_returns.shape[0]):
    sample = df_returns.iloc[(t-window):t,:]
    covmat = np.cov(sample.T,bias=True)
    U, s, V = np.linalg.svd(covmat)
    sv[count] = s[0]
    count = count + 1

ts_sv = pd.DataFrame({'DATE':df.iloc[(window+1): , 0],'SingularValue':sv})
ts_sv["DATE"] = pd.to_datetime(ts_sv["DATE"], format = "%m/%d/%Y")
